%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suryakumar%20to%20lead%20India%20in%20T20I%20series%20vs%20Australia%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700227223000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105295117%2Cimgsize-44038.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fsuryakumar-yadav-to-lead-india-in-five-match-t20i-series-vs-australia-reports%2Farticleshow%2F105294486.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%20continues%20to%20recuperate%20from%20an%20ankle%20injury%2C%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20could%20lead%20Team%20India%20in%20the%20upcoming%20T20I%20home%20series%20against%20Australia%2C%20according%20to%20a%20media%20report.%20The%20five-match%20T20%20series%20will%20begin%20on%20November%2023%20in%20Vizag%20and%20conclude%20in%20Hyderabad%20on%20December%203.%20According%20to%20a%20media%20report%2C%20the%20selecting%20committee%2C%20headed%20by%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20is%20likely%20to%20elevate%20Suryakumar%20to%20the%20captaincy%20as%20Pandya%20was%20ruled%20out%20due%20to%20an%20injury%20he%20sustained%20during%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20and%20will%20take%20at%20least%20two%20months%20to%20recover%20fully%20from%20his%20ankle%20injury.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'India%2065%20all%20out'%3A%20Marsh's%20bold%20WC%20final%20prediction%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700227128000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105295082%2Cimgsize-33006.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-world-cup%2Fnews%2Faustralia-450%2F2-india-65-all-out-mitchell-marshs-bold-world-cup-final-prediction-takes-social-media-by-storm%2Farticleshow%2F105295075.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20India%20all%20set%20to%20take%20on%20Australia%20in%20what%20promises%20to%20be%20a%20thrilling%20World%20Cup%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%20on%20Sunday%2C%20all-rounder%20Mitchell%20Marsh's%20prediction%20for%20the%20summit%20clash%2C%20which%20he%20made%20earlier%20this%20year%20during%20IPL%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20As%20the%20two-time%20champions%20India%20set%20their%20eyes%20on%20a%20third%20title%20and%20second%20on%20home%20soil%2C%20formidable%20Australia%20and%20the%20five-time%20champions%20stand%20in%20their%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Congress%20Has%20an%20Edge%20Over%20BJP%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F17192201%2FF8oD1roWcAAOHje.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20in%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20quoted%20from%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20veteran%20LK%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20memoir%20where%20he%20apparently%20said%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Coriginal%20laboratory%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20BJP-Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20was%20not%20Gujarat%2C%20but%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20election%20bound%20state%20is%20witnessing%20a%20fierce%20electoral%20battle%20%C2%A0to%20preserve%20its%20laboratory%20so%20that%20its%20prospects%20to%20win%20the%20general%20elections%20of%202024%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%20remain%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20ruling%20the%20state%20for%20the%20last%2018%20years%20under%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%2C%20is%20not%20sure%20of%20winning%20the%20assembly%20elections%20and%20has%20therefore%20strategised%20its%20election%20campaign%20around%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20This%20strategy%20is%20part%20of%20a%20familiar%20pattern%20that%20the%20party%20has%20adopted%20before%20many%20other%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20centrality%20in%20state%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20predominantly%20common%20theme%20adopted%20by%20the%20BJP%20%C2%A0in%20all%20state%20elections%2C%20be%20it%20Karnataka%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20now%20in%20poll%20bound%20States%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20MP%20and%20Telangana%2C%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20centrality%20for%20seeking%20votes%20of%20the%20electorate%20in%20complete%20disregard%20of%20regional%20leaders%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20unmistakably%20demonstrated%20in%20MP%20where%20the%20BJP%20publicity%20vehicles%20and%20election%20programmes%C2%A0%20play%20the%20song%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EModi%20ke%20mann%20mein%20basey%20MP%2C%20MP%20ke%20mann%20mein%20Modi.%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D(MP%20is%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Modi%2C%20and%20Modi%20is%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20MP).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17-300x164.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F07091746%2FScreenshot-2023-11-07-at-9.14.17-1024x559.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22655%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPM%20Narendra%20Modi%20at%20an%20election%20rally.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40narendramodi%2Fvideo%20screengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFielding%20BJP%20MPs%20and%20Union%20ministers%20to%20contest%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20had%20to%20wait%20for%20getting%20a%20ticket%20when%20the%20party%20declared%20its%20third%20list%20of%20candidates.%20Even%20the%20prime%20minister%20did%20not%20mention%20his%20name%20in%20the%20meetings%20addressed%20by%20him%20in%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20presence%20even%20when%20the%20two%20shared%20a%20dias.%20Surprisingly%2C%20BJP%20MPs%20such%20as%20Rakesh%20Singh%20(former%20state%20BJP%20president)%2C%20Ganesh%20Singh%2C%20Reeti%20Pathak%20and%20Uday%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20apart%20from%20general%20secretary%20Kailash%20Vijayvargiya%2C%20have%20been%20fielded%20to%20contest%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20More%20surprising%20is%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20names%20of%20several%20senior%20Union%20ministers%20such%20as%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Prahlad%20Patel%20and%20Faggan%20Singh%20Kulaste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20announcements%20were%20interpreted%20by%20the%20media%20as%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20open%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20post%20to%20several%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20party%2C%20putting%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20chances%20at%20stake%20who%20has%20served%20the%20state%20for%2018%20years.%20Eventually%2C%20Chouhan%20prevailed%20and%20got%20the%20BJP%20ticket%20to%20contest%20elections%20after%20he%2C%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20presence%2C%20asked%20people%20in%20an%20election%20rally%20if%20they%20wanted%20him%20back%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20if%20Modi%20was%20their%20preferred%20choice%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F684780%2Fmadhya-pradesh-election-ravidas-temple-dalit-jobs%2F%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Ravidas%20Temple%20Is%20Fine%2C%20But%20What%20About%20Jobs%20and%20Education%3F%E2%80%99%20Ask%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Dalits%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prospects%20for%20BJP%20appear%20not%20so%20bright%20in%20MP%20because%20of%20the%20calculated%20manner%20in%20which%20regional%20leadership%20of%20the%20state%20has%20been%20relegated%20to%20a%20secondary%20status.%20Exactly%20the%20same%20thing%20was%20done%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20where%20the%20BJP%20lost.%20It%20is%20contrary%20to%20RSS%20mouthpiece%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fem%3Eeditorial%20which%20categorically%20stated%20that%20after%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20defeat%C2%A0%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20and%20Hindutva%20alone%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20get%20votes%20for%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20factions%20within%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegional%20leaders%E2%80%99%20neglect%20combined%20with%20the%20internecine%20fights%20among%20different%20factions%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20MP%20has%20considerably%20weakened%20its%20unity%20and%20solidarity%20in%20facing%20the%20anti-incumbency%20problem%20confronted%20by%20the%20Chouhan%20Government.%20It%20is%20widely%20reported%20in%20media%20that%20there%20are%20three%20factions%20within%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20BJP-%20Shivaraj%2C%20%3Cem%3Emaharaj%3C%2Fem%3E%20(ruler)%20and%20%3Cem%3Enaaraz%3C%2Fem%3E%20(angry).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Shivraj%20faction%20is%20attributed%20to%20Chouhan%2C%20the%20maharaj%20faction%20is%20headed%20by%20Jyotiraditya%20Scindia%2C%20the%20erstwhile%20scion%20of%20the%20royal%20family%20of%20Gwalior%2C%20and%20the%20naaraz%20faction%20which%20consists%20of%20those%20dissatisfied%20and%20angry%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20workers%20who%2C%20in%20spite%20of%20their%20long%20years%20of%20association%20with%20the%20party%2C%20were%20sidelined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20faction%20ridden%20party%20with%20its%20regional%20leaders%20completely%20neglected%20by%20the%20central%20leadership%20has%20found%20itself%20in%20a%20disadvantageous%20position%20to%20take%20on%20the%20relatively%20unified%20Congress%20which%20relied%20solely%20on%20a%20Madhya%20Pradesh-centric%20leader%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20to%20prepare%20its%20electoral%20strategy%20and%20put%20a%20decisive%20challenge%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHindutva%20as%20a%20strategic%20failure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindutva%20has%20failed%20to%20gain%20traction%20in%20MP%20in%20spite%20of%20aggressive%20campaigning%20by%20several%20BJP%20leaders.%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%E2%80%99s%20completion%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20even%20went%20to%20the%20extent%20of%20saying%20that%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20if%20voted%20to%20power%2C%20would%20arrange%20a%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(veiwing)%20of%20the%20deity%20for%20the%20people%20of%20MP%20at%20no%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F27124559%2FF64MDKrXYAAbRfI-1024x576.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-677110%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40rameshbidhuri%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELegendary%20Olympian%20Aslam%20Sherkhan%2C%20who%20played%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20in%201975%20when%20India%20won%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20later%20served%20as%20a%20Congress%20leader%20and%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Minority%20Affairs%2C%20said%20that%20Hindutva%20would%20never%20determine%20politics%20in%20MP%20because%20the%20tribal%20community%20and%20other%20backward%20classes%20(OBCs)%20make%20up%20for%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20MP%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20Hindutva%20is%20not%20major%20attraction%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20seems%20to%20be%20right%20in%20his%20assessment.%20There%20is%20an%20apparent%20failure%20of%20Hindutva%20as%20a%20strategy%20in%20MP%20where%20people%20are%20more%20bothered%20about%20the%20massive%20corruption%20alleged%20to%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20BJP%20government%20under%20Chouhan.%20They%20are%20equally%20concerned%20about%20the%20rising%20inflation%20and%20unemployment%20levels%20and%20that%20way%20this%20is%20impacting%20livelihood%20opportunities.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20caste%20survey%20details%20coming%20out%20of%20Bihar%20has%20hugely%20drawn%20the%20attention%20of%20MP%E2%80%99s%20OBCs%20which%20also%20include%20Muslims.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20assertion%20that%20caste%20census%20of%20the%20state%20would%20be%20carried%20when%20Congress%20assumes%20power%20is%20further%20derailing%20the%20Hindutva%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFifty%20Percent%20Government%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20Congress%20made%20%E2%80%9C40%25%20sarkara%E2%80%9D%20a%20campaign%20plank%20to%20awaken%20people%20about%20the%2040%25%20commission%20taken%20by%20government%20agencies%20under%20the%20BJP%20rule%20there%2C%20the%20party%20has%20launched%20a%20blistering%20attack%20on%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20MP%20and%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9C50%25%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2F682494%2Fwhy-bjps-hindutva-campaign-is-not-working-in-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%3EWhy%20The%20Hindutva%20Card%20is%20Not%20Working%20for%20BJP%20in%20Poll-Bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20driven%20home%20by%20the%20party%20is%20that%2050%25%20commission%20is%20allegedly%20taken%20by%20the%20Chouhan%20Government.%20This%20has%20incensed%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20so%20much%20that%20several%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20who%20first%20raised%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ujjain%E2%80%99s%20Mahakal%20Temple%20corridor%2C%20which%20was%20unveiled%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20October%202022%2C%20six%20out%20of%20the%20seven%20Saptrishi%20statues%20fell%20from%20their%20pedestals%20due%20to%20wind%20speed.%20Congress%20sharply%20criticised%20BJP%20Government%20for%20not%20even%20sparing%20the%20gods%20from%20the%20tentacles%20of%20its%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVery%20strikingly%20all%20such%20charges%20are%20sticking%20and%20greatly%20embarrassing%20the%20Chouhan%20government%20leading%20to%20a%20growing%20perception%20that%20the%20BJP%20regime%20is%20deeply%20mired%20in%20corruption.%20To%20add%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20troubled%20in%20MP%2C%20three%20videos%20showing%20Union%20agriculture%20minister%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%E2%80%99s%20son%20allegedly%20dealing%20with%20hundreds%20of%20crores%20of%20money%20with%20a%20foreign%20national%20has%20bolstered%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20riddled%20with%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20such%20a%20sordid%20backdrop%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospect%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20favourable.%20But%20one%20has%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20assembly%20elections%20to%20see%20if%20the%20opinion%20polls%20giving%20advantage%20to%20Congress%20over%20BJP%20are%20true%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.%20N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K%20R%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700226011000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2F