0that%20he%20had%20asked%20the%20ChatGpt%20team%20to%20flag%20deepfakes%20and%20put%20out%20a%20warning%20when%20such%20videos%20were%20circulated%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20illustrated%20his%20point%20by%20citing%20a%20deepfake%20video%20of%20him%20doing%20Garba%2C%20a%20festival%20dance%20of%20Gujarat%20that%20is%20popular%20across%20the%20country.%20%26quot%3BI%20recently%20saw%20a%20video%20in%20which%20I%20was%20seen%20playing%20Garba.%20I%20have%20not%20done%20Garba%20since%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20other%20such%20videos%20online%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20PM%20Modi%2C%20addressing%20journalists%20at%20the%20Diwali%20Milan%20programme%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20urged%20the%20media%20to%20educate%20people%20on%20such%20fake%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20times%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20technology%20should%20be%20used%20responsibly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20cautioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20remarks%20come%20amid%20consternation%20and%20outrage%20about%20a%20series%20of%20deepfake%20videos%20on%20social%20media%20with%20morphed%20faces%20of%20actors%20Rashmika%20Mandanna%2C%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20Kajol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20videos%20have%20sparked%20massive%20worry%20about%20fake%20videos%20targeting%20public%20figures%20and%20the%20power%20of%20AI%20to%20create%20deepfakes%20that%20can%20mislead%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Esparked%20concerns%20over%20the%20ramifications%20of%20such%20tinkering%2C%20especially%20for%20public%20figures%2C%20who%20may%20get%20in%20trouble%20over%20visuals%20their%20faces%20are%20doctored%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20voices%20in%20the%20film%20industry%2C%20including%20legendary%20actor%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20have%20called%20for%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20a