2%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20How%20ChatGPT%20Algorithm%20Is%20Used%20to%20Make%20Deepfakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20addressed%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20misuse%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeepfakes%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0Addressing%20journalists%20at%20BJP's%20Diwali%20Milan%20programme%20at%20the%20party's%20headquarters%20in%20Delhi%2C%20PM%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-says-deepfake-a-big-concern-asked-chatgpt-team-to-give-deepfake-warning-in-content-4581834%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20times%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20technology%20should%20be%20used%20responsibly.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20recently%20saw%20a%20video%20in%20which%20I%20was%20seen%20singing%20a%20Garba%20song.%20There%20are%20many%20other%20such%20videos%20online.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi's%20comment%20comes%20days%20after%20deepfake%20videos%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-rashmika-mandanna-and-katrina-kaif-kajols-deepfake-video-surfaces-online-4581316%5C%22%3ERashmika%20Mandanna%20and%20Katrina%20Kaif%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0surfaced%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20are%20deepfake%20videos%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepfake%20videos%20involve%20the%20use%20of%20synthetic%20media%20to%20replace%20a%20person%20in%20an%20existing%20image%20or%20video.%20It%20typically%20uses%20generative%20models%20and%20advanced%20techniques%20in%20computer%20vision%2C%20often%20distinct%20from%20language%20models%20like%20ChatGPT.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20is%20the%20ChatGPT%20algorithm%20used%20to%20make%20deepfake%20videos%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDeepfakes%20are%20created%20through%20a%20combination%20of%20machine%20learning%20techniques%2C%20particularly%20using%20generative%20models%20like%20Generative%20Adversarial%20Networks%20(GANs)%20and%20deep%20neural%20networks.%20The%20first%20step%20entails%20gathering%20a%20large%20dataset%20of%20images%20or%20videos%20featuring%20the%20target%20person%20whose%20likeness%20will%20be%20used%20in%20the%20deepfake.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDeepfake%20technology%20uses%20rules%20and%20labelled%20data%20to%20break%20down%20sentences.%20These%20algorithms%20can%20understand%20simple%20commands%2C%20as%20seen%20in%20chatbots%20and%20voice%20assistants.%20However%2C%20they%20pose%20a%20cybersecurity%20risk%20through%20text%20analysis%20and%20sentence%20structuring%2C%20particularly%20in%20actions%20like%20enquiring%20about%20%26quot%3Bwhat%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwhen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGenerative%20models%2C%20such%20as%20GANs%2C%20are%20trained%20on%20the%20preprocessed%20data.%20GANs%20consist%20of%20a%20generator%20and%20a%20discriminator.%20The%20generator%20creates%20synthetic%20content%2C%20and%20the%20discriminator%20evaluates%20its%20realism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOnce%20the%20model%20is%20trained%2C%20it%20can%20be%20used%20to%20generate%20deepfake%20content.%20For%20videos%2C%20the%20model%20might%20need%20to%20consider%20temporal%20aspects%20to%20create%20realistic%20facial%20expressions%20and%20movements.%20ChatGPT%20might%20be%20used%20to%20make%20deepfake%20videos%20with%20speech%20that%20sounds%20just%20like%20a%20real%20person%2C%20making%20the%20fake%20video%20more%20believable.%20Deepfake%20videos%20or%20images%20may%20undergo%20post-processing%20to%20enhance%20realism%2C%20adjust%20lighting%2C%20or%20refine%20details.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20tackle%20these%20concerns%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20create%20tools%20for%20spotting%20deepfake%20videos%20and%20boost%20AI%20literacy%20among%20the%20public.%20Establishing%20legal%20frameworks%20may%20be%20necessary%20to%20control%20the%20use%20of%20deepfake%20technology%20and%20prevent%20misuse.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700219760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fsj5lbf58_chatgpt-_625x300_15_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-chatgpt-algorithm-is-used-to-make-deepfakes-4582350%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Friday%20addressed%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20misuse%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20%26quot%3Bdeepfakes%26quot%3B.%20PM%20Modi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BDuring%20the%20times%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20technology%20should%20be%20us%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-chatgpt-algorithm-is-used-to-make-deepfakes-4582350%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-chatgpt-algorithm-is-used-to-make-deepfakes-4582350%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexplained-how-chatgpt-algorithm-is-used-to-make-deepfakes-4582350%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dana%20Carvey%3A%20Wayne's%20World%20star's%20son%20Dex%20dies%20aged%2032%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700219475000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F98C1%2Fproduction%2F_131750193_gettyimages-1153312838-2.jpg%22%2C%2