D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsaLJXnAcKK%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FsaLJXnAcKK%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Rabbi%20Shmuley%20(%40RabbiShmuley)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRabbiShmuley%2Fstatus%2F1724986121392636052%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRabbiShmuley%2Fstatus%2F1724988873707507939%5C%22%3Eseparate%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20wrote%20that%20the%20tourist%20%26quot%3Bwas%20actually%20murdered%20after%20being%20tortured%2C%20and%20who%20knows%20what%20else%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHamas%20are%20evil%20incarnate.%20They%20are%20the%20Nazis%20of%20our%20time.%20Whoever%20denies%2C%20after%20witnessing%20what%20they%20did%20to%20this%20poor%20innocent%20woman%2C%20that%20Hamas%20does%20not%20need%20to%20be%20completely%20destroyed%20is%20immoral%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20rabbi's%20claims%20have%20not%20been%20officially%20confirmed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF).%20It%20was%20also%20not%20clear%20which%20of%20the%20four%20men%20pictured%20with%20Ms%20Louk's%20body%20the%20rabbi%20was%20referring%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fworld-news%2F2023%2F11%2F16%2Fhamas-fighter-who-paraded-shani-louk-body-in-gaza-dead-sasy%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20carried%20a%20larger%20excerpt%20of%20the%20alleged%20conversation%20of%20Ms%20Louk's%20mother%20Ricarda%20with%20the%20rabbi%20where%20she%20said%20there%20is%20one%20less%20bad%20person%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20happy%20that%20this%20person%20cannot%20hurt%20anyone%20else%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20matter%20so%20much%20because%20it's%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2053-year-old%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20a%20typical%20murder%20story%20where%20you%20find%20the%20murderer%20and%20they%20got%20killed%20-%20they%20did%20those%20things%20as%20a%20group%2C%20so%20one%20doesn't%20make%20so%20much%20difference%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mrs%20Louk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShani%20Louk's%20family%20kept%20its%20hopes%20alive%20for%20weeks%2C%20believing%20that%20she%20was%20alive%20and%20in%20a%20hospital%20in%20Gaza.%20But%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20later%20confirmed%20that%20DNA%20found%20on%20a%20piece%20of%20skull%20matched%20Ms%20Louk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Louk%2C%20a%20tattoo%20artist%2C%20had%20German%20and%20Israeli%20citizenship.%20She%20lived%20in%20Israel%20but%20spent%20part%20of%20her%20childhood%20in%20Portland%2C%20Oregon%2C%20where%20she%20attended%20kindergarten%20at%20the%20Jewish%20Portland%20Academy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700217120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fmqr7hhto_shani-louk_625x300_30_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froasting-in-hell-rabbi-says-hamas-operative-who-paraded-german-tourist-dead-4582422%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shani%20Louk%20was%20kidnapped%20form%20a%20music%20festival%20on%20October%207%20and%20her%20body%20was%20found%20weeks%20later.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froasting-in-hell-rabbi-says-hamas-operative-who-paraded-german-tourist-dead-4582422%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froasting-in-hell-rabbi-says-hamas-operative-who-paraded-german-tourist-dead-4582422%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Froasting-in-hell-rabbi-says-hamas-operative-who-paraded-german-tourist-dead-4582422%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boy%20dies%20by%20suicide%20as%20dad%20takes%20away%20cellphone%22