%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20constant%20communication%20is%20being%20maintained%20with%20them%2C%20ensuring%20their%20spirits%20remain%20unbroken%20and%20their%20hope%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20have%20been%20trapped%20inside%20the%20tunnel%20since%20Sunday%20morning%20when%20a%20part%20of%20the%20under-construction%20structure%20near%20Uttarkashi%20collapsed%20following%20a%20landslide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20tunnel%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%2C%20a%20national%20infrastructure%20initiative%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%2C%20and%20Yamunotri.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700216100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F44ba8r8g_uttarakhand-tunnel-pti-_625x300_16_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-tunnel-rescue-whats-causing-a-delay-in-rescue-of-40-trapped-workers-official-explains-4582299%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rescue%20workers%20have%20drilled%20up%20to%2025%20metres%20through%20the%20rubble%20to%20reach%20the%20workers%20trapped%20inside%20a%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%20for%20over%20120%20hours.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-tunnel-rescue-whats-causing-a-delay-in-rescue-of-40-trapped-workers-official-explains-4582299%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-tunnel-rescue-whats-causing-a-delay-in-rescue-of-40-trapped-workers-official-explains-4582299%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarkashi-tunnel-tunnel-rescue-whats-causing-a-delay-in-rescue-of-40-trapped-workers-official-explains-4582299%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20PC%20Imports%20Surge%20to%204.5%20million%20After%20Union%20Government%20U-Turn%20on%20Import%20Licenses%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F10125800%2FUntitled-design.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20imports%20of%20personal%20computers%20surged%20to%20a%20record%204.5%20million%20units%20in%20the%20July%20to%20September%20quarter%2C%20recording%20an%20increase%20of%2014%25%20year-over-year%20(YoY)%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.idc.com%2Fgetdoc.jsp%3FcontainerId%3DprAP51395423%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20Data%20Corporation%20(IDC)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Worldwide%20Quarterly%20Personal%20Computing%20Device%20Tracker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20data%20released%20on%20November%2016%2C%20the%20notebook%20category%20grew%20by%2013.1%25%20YoY%2C%20while%20the%20desktop%20category%20grew%20by%2019.3%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20traditional%20PC%20market%20includes%20desktops%2C%20notebooks%2C%20and%20workstations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20growth%20comes%20after%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-a-u-turn-union-govt-rolls-back-plans-to-license-laptop-computer-imports%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EU-turn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month%20on%20its%20earlier%20plan%20imposing%20import%20restrictions%20on%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20announcement%20on%20October%2019%2C%20came%20months%20after%20the%20government%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fgovt-imposes-import-curbs-on-laptops-computers-with-immediate-effect%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimposed%20import%20restrictions%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20certain%20types%20of%20computers%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Csecurity%20reasons%E2%80%9D%20and%20the%20need%20to%20promote%20domestic%20manufacturing%20on%20August%203.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20then%20had%20also%20said%20that%20those%20wanting%20to%20import%20these%20items%20would%20need%20a%20license%20starting%20November%201.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20consumer%20segment%20saw%20strong%20traction%20in%203Q23%20after%20a%20challenging%20past%20four%20quarters.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20government%20of%20India%20declared%20a%20mandatory%20requirement%20of%20import%20licenses%20for%20PCs%20from%2030%20October.%20Though%20this%20decision%20was%20later%20put%20on%20hold%2C%20vendors%20shipped%20significant%20channel%20inventory%20to%20avoid%20any%20risks%20of%20supply%20shortages%20or%20price%20hikes%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20ensuring%20sufficient%20supplies%20for%20festival%20season%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bharath%20Shenoy%2C%20senior%20research%20analyst%2C%20IDC%20India%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20IDC%20data%20the%20consumer%20sector%20saw%20a%20rise%20of%2026.3%25%20compared%20to%20the%20previous%20year%20but%20the%20commercial%20sector%20remained%20unchanged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20terms%20of%20personal%20computer%20companies%2C%20HP%20Inc.%20led%20the%20market%20with%20a%20share%20of%2029.4%25%20as%20it%20topped%20the%20charts%20in%20both%20the%20commercial%20and%20consumer%20segments%20with%20shares%20of%2034.3%25%20and%2025.9%25%20respectively%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20IDC%20the%20firm%E2%80%99s%20inventory%20pushes%20and%20positive%20market%20sentiment%20helped%20it%20clock%20its%20biggest%20ever%20consumer%20quarter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELenovo%20came%20second%20with%20a%20share%20of%2017%25%20as%20its%20shipments%20fell%208.8%25%20year%20on%20year.%20In%20the%20desktop%20category%20it%20fared%20well%20and%20witnessed%20year%20on%20year%20growth%20of%2032.5%25%20in%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDell%20Technologies%20came%20third%20with%20a%2014.6%25%20market%20share%20and%20a%20year-on-year%20growth%20of%203.8%25.%20IDC%20said%20that%20Lenovo%20had%20not%20decided%20not%20to%20do%20heavy%20stocking%2C%20which%20led%20to%20some%20market%20share%20loss%20but%20helped%20maintain%20healthy%20channel%20inventory.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EASUS%20took%20the%20fourth%20position%20with%20a%2012.5%25%20share%20and%20achieved%20its%20most%20significant%20consumer%20quarter%20by%20surpassing%20500%2C000%20units%20in%20the%20consumer%20segment.%20According%20to%20IDC%20ASUS%20decided%20to%20do%20heavy%20stocking%20for%20festive%20season%20sales%20as%20it%20wanted%20to%20avoid%20any%20supply%20hurdles%20due%20to%20the%20import%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcer%20took%20the%20fifth%20spot%20with%2011.6%25%20market%20share%20despite%20a%2020.9%25%20year-on-year%20growth.%20IDC%20said%20that%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20focus%20on%20online%20channels%20contributed%20to%20its%20most%20substantial%20consumer%20quarter%20on%20record.%20The%20firm%20pushed%20stocks%20on%20online%20channels%20and%20had%20its%20biggest%20consumer%20quarter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20consumer%20segment%2C%20IDC%20said%20that%20in%20the%20PC%20market%20a%20dearth%20of%20enterprise%20orders%20remains%20a%20concern.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20the%20PC%20market%20has%20seen%20a%20substantial%20channel%20push%20in%20the%20consumer%20segment%20and%20to%20some%20extent%20in%20the%20SME%20segment%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Navkendar%20Singh%2C%20Associate%20Vice%20President%2C%20Devices%20Research%2C%20IDC%20India%2C%20South%20Asia%20%26amp%3B%20ANZ.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20vendors%20are%20now%20focused%20on%20increasing%20their%20local%20assembly%20mix%20as%20government%20and%20education%20projects%20are%20expected%20to%20prefer%20locally%20assembled%20devices.%20While%20this%20might%20give%20a%20further%20boost%20to%20the%20government%20and%20education%20segments%2C%20a%20dearth%20of%20enterprise%20orders%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20concern%20as%20the%20enterprise%20segment%20is%20expected%20to%20decline%20by%20over%2020%25%20YoY%20in%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700215580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F10125800%2FUntitled-design.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-pc-imports-surge-to-4-5-million-after-union-government-u-turn-on-import-licenses%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20the%20International%20Data%20Corporation%2C%20vendors%20shipped%20significant%20channel%20inventory%20to%20avoid%20any%20risks%20of%20supply%20shortages%20or%20price%20hikes%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20ensuring%20sufficient%20supplies%20for%20festival%20season%20sales.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftrade%2Findias-pc-imports-surge-to-4-5-million-after-union-government-u-turn-on-import-licenses%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20change%20status%20from%20'commercial'%20to%20'private'%20for%20a%20second-hand%20car%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700215558000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105289370%2Cimgsize-21764.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fauto%2Fnews%2Fhow-to-change-status-from-commercial-to-private-for