summit%20on%20the%20elections%20and%20what%20the%20BJP%20has%20so%20far%20determined%20the%20results%20would%20be%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20he%20is%20confident%20the%20party%20will%20see%20a%20landslide%20win%20in%20Congress-ruled%20Rajasthan%2C%20while%20the%20party%20is%20%26quot%3Bclearly%20ahead%20in%20Chhattisgarh%26quot%3B%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20%26quot%3Bwill%20return%20to%20BJP%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpinion%20polls%20and%20analysts%20have%20predicted%20the%20BJP%20would%20win%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20lose%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20while%20Mizoram%20is%20unclear%20and%20the%20battle%20in%20Telangana%20is%20mainly%20between%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%2C%20however%2C%20dismissed%20these%20predictions%20as%20not%20reflecting%20the%20ground%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20clear%20what%20we%20see%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20TV%20and%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20leads%20me%20to%20believe%20the%20tide%20has%20turned%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20we%20are%20clearly%20ahead%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20even%20before%20I%20left%20India%2C%20was%20coming%20back%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20visited%20Rajasthan%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20extensively.%20Rajasthan%20is%20looking%20to%20be%20a%20one-sided%20affair%3B%20we%20are%20doing%20extremely%20well%20in%20Rajasthan.%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhatisgarh%20are%20poised%20to%20give%20BJP%20victories%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20he%20will%20be%20able%20to%20see%20the%20Telangana%20situation%20after%20he%20returns%20to%20India.%20%26quot%3BTelangana...%20voting%20is%20on%20November%2030.%20I%20have%20had%20only%20two%20visits%20to%20Telangana%20before%20coming%20here.%20Once%20am%20back%20and%20see%20the%20situation%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20I%20will%20get%20a%20better%20sense%20of%20what's%20happening%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20BJP%20will%20win%20in%20at%20least%20three%20states%20-%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20-%20where%20he%20had%20extensively%20campianed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tesla%20and%20EVs%20in%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20said%20his%20US%20visit%20was%20primarily%20for%20meeting%20the%20Tesla%20team%2C%20%26quot%3Bmany%20of%20whom%20are%20Indians%20who%20have%20done%20us%20proud.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20wants%20to%20discuss%20Tesla's%20plans%20about%20elements%20from%20India%20in%20their%20supply%20chain%2C%20especially%20after%20Tesla%20doubled%20their%20imports%20from%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20adopting%20electric%20vehicles%20(EVs)%20very%20fast.%20Nearly%2040%20per%20cent%20two-wheelers%20are%20EVs%20now.%20For%20commercial%20buses%20and%20cabs%2C%20it's%20a%20no-brainer%20to%20use%20EVs%3B%20it's%20much%20more%20economical%20and%20eco-friendly%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20private%20vehicles%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%20the%20battery%20costs%20are%20a%20deterrent%20but%20will%20hopefully%20see%20a%20rapid%20price%20correction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%20the%20fastest%20growth%20of%20EVs%20is%20likely%20to%20happen%20in%20India.%20The%20government%20has%20also%20bought%20a%20lot%20of%20EVs%2C%20I%20can%20see%20that%20on%20the%20roads%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20also%20met%20US%20leaders%20including%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20the%20APEC%20summit.%20He%20said%20India%20has%20not%20decided%20yet%20on%20whether%20to%20apply%20for%20joining%20the%20APEC.%20India%20had%20made%20a%20request%20to%20join%20the%20grouping%20in%201991.%20While%20a%20majority%20of%20members%20were%20in%20favour%20of%20India's%20inclusion%2C%20some%20opposed%20it%2C%20citing%20the%20country's%20record%20on%20economic%20reforms%20and%20claiming%20that%20it%20has%20%26quot%3Bprotectionist%20instincts%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700214900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fua861sfg_piyush-goyal_625x300_17_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-3-states-piyush-goyals-prediction-for-bjp-in-assembly-elections-4582315%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Piyush%20Goyal%20is%20in%20the%20US%20attending%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(APEC)%2C%20but%20is%20keeping%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20the%20assembly%20elections%20in%20five%20states%20back%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-3-states-piyush-goyals-prediction-for-bjp-in-assembly-elections-4582315%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-3-states-piyush-goyals-prediction-for-bjp-in-assembly-elections-4582315%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-3-states-piyush-goyals-prediction-for-bjp-in-assembly-elections-4582315%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Urges%20Canada%20to%20Abide%20By%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_in_New_Delhi_on_February_23_2018_1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20on%20Thursday%20(November%2016)%20reiterated%20its%20call%20for%20Canada%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20Vienna%20convention%20on%20diplomatic%20relations%20after%20pro-Khalistan%20groups%20allegedly%20disturbed%20a%20camp%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Indian%20consulate%20in%20Vancouver.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20consulate%20had%20set%20up%20a%20camp%20to%20provide%20life%20certificates%20to%20pensioners%20on%20November%2012%20as%20part%20of%20a%20routine%20exercise.%20External%20affairs%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Arindam%20Bagchi%2C%20during%20a%20media%20briefing%2C%20said%20that%20the%20event%20was%20held%20successfully%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edespite%20attempts%20by%20a%20few%20radical%20elements%20to%20cause%20trouble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDays%20after%20the%20event%2C%20India%20called%20on%20Ottawa%20to%20ensure%20a%20conducive%20environment%20in%20line%20with%20provisions%20of%20the%20Vienna%20convention%20on%20diplomatic%20relations%20so%20that%20its%20officials%20can%20discharge%20their%20duties%20without%20any%20hindrance%20or%20security%20concerns%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-calls-on-canada-to-respect-vienna-convention-on-diplomatic-relations-562949%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20reiterate%20the%20need%20for%20nations%20to%20respect%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20diplomatic%20relations%20so%20that%20our%20diplomats%20can%20discharge%20their%20diplomatic%20obligations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bagchi%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20paper%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20diplomatic%20relations%20with%20Canada%20had%20soured%20after%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20accused%20India%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20pro-Khalistan%20activist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar%20in%20September.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20strongly%20rejected%20the%20allegations%20and%20responded%20by%20temporarily%20suspending%20visa%20services%20to%20Canadian%20citizens%20and%20asked%20Ottawa%20to%20downsize%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20the%20country%20to%20ensure%20parity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBagchi%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20an%20incident%20that%20occurred%20near%20Brampton%20on%20Diwali%20which%20he%20called%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunrest%E2%80%9D%20between%20two%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20regards%20to%20events%20that%20you%20alluded%20to%20near%20Brampton%20on%20Diwali.%20I%20think%20that%20was%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20unrest%20between%20the%20two%20groups.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20there%20has%20been%20any%20complaint%20that%20our%20consulate%20has%20received%E2%80%A6%20I%20saw%20some%20social%20media%20reports.%20We%20also%20understand%20that%20the%20authorities%20there%20are%20looking%20into%20that%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findia-calls-on-canada-to-respect-vienna-convention-on-diplomatic-relations-562949%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20fresh%20call%20to%20Ottawa%20comes%20days%20after%20it%20urged%20Canada%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Funhrc-india-canada-universal-periodic-review%5C%22%3Estop%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmisuse%E2%80%9D%20of%20freedom%20of%20expression%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20incite%20violence%20and%20prevent%20activities%20of%20extremist%20groups%20during%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20review%20of%20human%20rights%20record%20at%20the%20UN%20Human%20Rights%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20call%20by%20India%20was%20presented%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Universal%20Periodic%20Review%20(UPR)%20process%2C%20under%20which%20member%20states%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20undergo%20a%20periodic%20evaluation%20of%20their%20human%20rights%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700214789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F21173817%2F1024px-The_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_with_the_Prime_Minister_of_Canada_Mr._Justin_Trudeau_at_Hyderabad_House_i