ar%20Mosque%20In%20Haryana's%20Nuh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20eight%20women%20were%20injured%20after%20unidentified%20people%20threw%20stones%20at%20them%20near%20a%20mosque%20in%20Haryana's%20Nuh%20on%20Thursday%20night%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20around%208%3A20%20pm%20when%20a%20group%20of%20women%20was%20on%20its%20way%20to%20perform%20a%20puja%20at%20a%20well.%20As%20the%20group%20neared%20the%20mosque%2C%20they%20were%20reportedly%20pelted%20with%20stones%2C%20causing%20injuries%20to%20eight%20women%2C%20police%20said.%20Nuh%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Narender%20Bijarniya%2C%20along%20with%20a%20significant%20police%20force%2C%20swiftly%20arrived%20at%20the%20location%20to%20calm%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20women%20were%20on%20their%20way%20to%20a%20'Kuan%20Poojan'%20and%20there%20has%20been%20a%20complaint%20that%20stones%20were%20pelted%20by%20some%20children%20from%20a%20madrasa%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bijarniya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nuh%20police%20official%20said%20an%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20while%20three%20of%20the%20children%20were%20identified%20and%20taken%20into%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETensions%20ran%20high%20in%20the%20communally%20charged%20town%2C%20with%20police%20deployed%20around%20the%20mosque%20and%20the%20main%20market%20of%20Nuh%20town%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20erupted%20soon%20after%20news%20of%20the%20incident%20reached%20locals%2C%20however%2C%20senior%20police%20officials%20and%20Nuh%20MLA%20Aftab%20Ahmed%20reached%20the%20spot%20and%20urged%20everyone%20to%20remain%20calm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENuh%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20major%20communal%20incident%20when%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20clashes%20that%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20Muslim-majority%20town%20on%20July%2031%20this%20year%2C%20when%20a%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Par