tion%20has%20made%20to%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20latter%20cannot%20refuse%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fat-2-plus-2-meet-us-asks-india-to-join-canada-probe-both-sides-support-israel%5C%22%3EUS%20Asks%20India%20to%20Join%20Canada%E2%80%99s%20Probe%2C%20Both%20Jointly%20Express%20Support%20For%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20such%20a%20massive%20shift%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20military%20policies%20needs%20to%20be%20correlated%20with%20the%20fundamental%20postulates%20of%20foreign%20policy.%20But%20call%20it%20%E2%80%9Cbipartisan%20consensus%E2%80%9D%20or%20whatever%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20main%20Opposition%20party%20apparently%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20care.%20This%20is%20not%20surprising.%20The%20shift%20is%20actually%20about%20a%20nascent%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E-US%20alliance%20to%20counter%20China%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20is%20a%20policy%20front%20where%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20choose%20between%20Tweedledum%20and%20Tweedledee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20China%20understand%20that%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20is%20transitioning%2C%20but%20they%20pretend%20not%20to%20notice.%20At%20any%20rate%2C%20their%20capacity%20to%20leverage%20Indian%20policies%20has%20dramatically%20shrunk%20%E2%80%94%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20in%20particular.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0is%20not%20ecstatic%20about%20growing%20multipolarity.%20It%20is%20a%20beneficiary%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Crules-based%20order%E2%80%9D%20and%20feels%20far%20more%20comfortable%20with%20a%20bipolar%20world%20in%20which%20the%20US%20is%20pre-eminent%2C%20developing%20its%20national%20power%20with%20China%E2%80%99s%20hegemonic%20instincts%20in%20check.%20Today%2C%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20willingness%20to%20align%20with%20the%20US%20is%20more%20evident%20than%20ever%20befor