0Most%20important%2C%20the%20joint%20statement%20omits%20any%20reference%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cright%20to%20self-defence%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20mantra%20that%20is%20constantly%20on%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20lips.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%20cannot%20possibly%20call%20the%20Gaza%20war%20an%20act%20of%20%E2%80%9Cself%20defence%E2%80%9D%20when%20Israel%20has%20unleashed%20such%20a%20brutal%20military%20operation%20against%20hapless%20civilians%20and%20razed%20Gaza%20City%20to%20the%20ground.%20It%E2%80%99s%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20joint%20British-American%20aerial%20bombing%20attack%20on%20Dresden%20during%20World%20War%20II%2C%20which%20killed%20over%2025%2C000%20German%20people%20on%20the%20night%20of%20March%209-10%2C%201945.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20all%20these%20diplomatic%20peregrinations%20through%20the%20Valley%20of%20Death%20could%20be%20better%20understood%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20the%20intense%20back-channel%20dealings%20involving%20the%20Hamas%20leadership%20in%20regional%20capitals%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Biden%20administration%20would%20have%20high%20stakes%20and%20is%20a%20participant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EM.K.%20Bhadrakumar%20is%20a%20retired%20diplomat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%2C%20excerpted%20from%20Indianpunchline.com%C2%A0was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1700198255000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17103838%2FF-kDD_eXcAAwo98-e1700197751446.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fin-two-months-india-transitioned-from-aspiring-global-