cal%20part%20in%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Dalits%20form%20the%20second%20largest%20community%20of%20voters%20in%20Tijara%2C%20after%20the%20Mev%20Muslims.%20In%20a%20close%20contest%20in%202018%20the%20BSP%E2%80%99s%20Sanjeev%20Yadav%20defeated%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20Aimaduudin%20Durru%20Mian%20with%20a%20thin%20margin%20of%203%25.%20Which%20is%20why%2C%20Balaknath%20is%20ensuring%20that%20his%20campaign%20takes%20him%20to%20as%20many%20Dalit%20villages%20he%20can%20go%20to%20on%20any%20given%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17085213%2FCrowd-watching-Tapookra-JPG-1-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-685133%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECrowd%20watching%20Tapookra.%20Photo%3A%20Ananta%20Jain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Nimahedi%20village%2C%20as%20a%20group%20of%20women%20begin%20to%20complain%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20drinking%20water%2C%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20men%20nudge%20them%20to%20touch%20his%20feet%20and%20seek%20the%20%E2%80%9CBaba%E2%80%99s%20blessings.%E2%80%9D%20In%20his%20speech%20Balaknath%20asks%20them%20to%20%E2%80%9Crise%20above%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bcaste%5D%20help%20protect%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esanatan%20dharm%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20something%20he%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20in%20his%20own%20campaign.%20Over%20the%20past%2030%20years%20the%20BJP%20has%20managed%20the%20paradoxical%20feat%20of%20appealing%20to%20an%20overarching%20Hindu%20identity%20while%20catering%20to%20the%20fragmentary%20demand%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaati%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20politics.%20This%20remains%20true%20of%20the%20Balakanth%20campaign%20who%20has%2C%20in%20part%2C%20been%20picked%20to%20contest%20from%20Tijara%20because%20he%20is%20a%20Yadav%2C%20who%20form%20the%20third%20largest%20community%20here.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEach%20time%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20convoy%20travels%20past%20the%20Yadav%20villages%2C%20the%20songs%20blaring%20from%20the%20DJ%20truck%20change.%20The%20lyrics%20now%20emphasise%20the%20caste%20identity%20of%20Balaknath%E2%80%99s%20family%20%E2%80%93%20his%20mother%20Urmila%20Devi%20and%20father%20Subhash%20Yadav.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20music%20makes%20me%20recall%20what%20Shahun%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Mewati%20Yuva%20Sangathan%2C%20had%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20Y%20%2B%20M%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20here%20it%20becomes%20Y%20versus%20M.%20Yadavs%20elsewhere%20in%20the%20country%20speak%20of%20Samajwad%2C%20here%20they%20target%20Muslim.%E2%80%9D%20The%20constituency%20has%20seen%20the%20battle%20between%20the%20Mevs%20and%20the%20Yadavs%20play%20ever%20since%20Independence%2C%20with%20the%20Mevs%20winning%20seven%20out%20of%2012%20assembly%20elections%2C%20and%20the%20Yadavs%20the%20other%20five.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAssured%20of%20Yadav%20backing%2C%20Balaknath%20knows%20the%20Dalits%20hold%20his%20electoral%20fate%20in%20their%20hand.%20We%20continue%20following%20the%20Balaknath%20convoy.%20At%20Bhamraka%20village%2C%20at%20the%20temple%2C%20addressing%20villagers%2C%20he%20evokes%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20but%20makes%20sure%20he%20refers%20to%20Babasahab%20Ambedkar%20as%20well%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20Babasaheb%20Ambedkar%2C%20the%20only%20other%20law%20minister%20from%20your%20community%20that%20the%20country%20has%20seen%20is%20Arjun%20Singh%20Meghwal.%20The%20BJP%20gave%20him%20this%20position%2C%20it%20was%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20decision.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20repeats%20this%20in%20village%20after%20village%2C%20ending%20his%20speeches%20with%20chants%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-jai-shri-ram-as-a-political-slogan-is-a-cover-for-violence%5C%22%3EJai%20Shri%20Ram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Ratan%20Baba%20Saheb%20Ambedkar%20Amar%20Rahe%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%20ki%20Jai%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20prominence%20given%20to%20Arjun%20Singh%20Meghwal%20in%20Rajasthan%20campaign%20ties%20in%20directly%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20Meghwals%20make%20up%20around%2025%20%25%20of%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20population%20and%20have%20growing%20sense%20of%20their%20assertion%20as%20a%20community.%20While%20much%20of%20Meghwal%20politics%20plays%20out%20in%20western%20Rajasthan%2C%20Jodhpur%20and%20Marwar%2C%20here%20in%20Tijara%2C%20the%20Meghwals%20form%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20Dalit%20electorate%20and%20here%2C%20this%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20appeal%C2%A0%20to%20the%20larger%20Dalit%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F17084425%2FF_DBNXRbcAAoIye.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcs