0anti-Balaknath%20slogans%20during%20his%20election%20sabha.%20The%20Sikhs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fanti-minority-stand-sgpc-bjp-leader-hate-speech-sandeep-dayma%5C%22%3Eremain%20angry%20at%20Sandeep%20Dayama%2C%20a%20prominent%20BJP%20Gujjar%20leader%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fbjp-gurdwaras-comment-rajasthan-assembly-polls-9012323%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehate%20speech%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CA%20large%20number%20of%20gurdwaras%20have%20come%20up%20recently%20in%20Tijara%E2%80%A6so%20it%20is%20our%20religious%20responsibility%20to%20uproot%20these%20open%20sores%20from%20here.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDayama%20was%20asked%20to%20leave%20the%20party%20and%20later%20retracted%20his%20statement%20and%20apologised%20with%20a%20clarification%20which%20was%20as%20hateful%20%E2%80%93%20he%20said%20he%20meant%20%E2%80%9Cmasjids%20and%20mazhars%2C%E2%80%9D%20not%20gurdwaras.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDaya%20Chand%20and%20his%20brothers%20also%20speak%20of%20a%20new%20factor%20that%20is%20generating%20interest.%20Udmiram%2C%20a%20Gujjar%20sarpanch%20has%20joined%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20Aazad%E2%80%99s%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20or%20ASPA%2C%20which%20is%20in%20a%20coalition%20with%20Hanuman%20Beniwal%20Rashtriya%20Loktantrik%20Party.%20In%20a%20cluster%20of%20Gujjar%20homes%20in%20Milakpur%2C%20people%20speak%20with%20some%20excitement%20at%20the%20prospects%20of%20a%20man%20from%20their%20community%20challenging%20the%20Yadav%20domination%20of%20the%20region.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20about%20Mahant%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20vote%20for%20Baba%20Balaknath%20to%20prove%20we%20are%20Hindus.%20If%20his%20supporters%20talk%20about%20him%20being%20a%20Yadav%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20we%20support%20our