m%20Saini%20ties%20back%20to%20a%20recent%20incident%20that%20served%20to%20magnify%20the%20politics%20of%20polarisation%20Balaknath%20represents.%20Saini%20was%20arrested%2C%20along%20with%20three%20others%20after%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fyouth-thrashed-over-remark-on-bajrang-dal-dies-in-rajasthan%2Farticleshow%2F103647440.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ekilling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%2020-year-old%20Wakeel%20Mohammad.%20The%20Muslim%20youth%20was%20abducted%20and%20beaten%20to%20death%20after%20a%20clash%20over%20allegations%20that%20he%E2%80%99d%C2%A0%20been%20made%20about%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal.%20Saini%20is%20a%20local%20advocate%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20other%20Hindutva%20groups%20have%20attacked%20Gehlot%20for%20appeasing%20Muslim%20sentiments%20by%20wrongly%20jailing%20him.%20Bane%20Singh%20says%20the%20Saini%20community%20are%20upset%20and%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20especially%20when%20they%20get%20Purshottam%20released%20shortly%20before%20the%20elections.%20When%20asked%20how%20they%20will%20do%20this%2C%20he%20smiles%2C%20shaking%20his%20head%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDekhtey%20raho%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bkeep%20watching%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20if%20on%20cue%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20he%20had%20referred%20to%2C%20Deshpal%20arrives%20at%20the%20hotel.%20Over%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20he%20tells%20us%20how%20the%20Congress%20banished%20him%20when%20he%20protested%20against%20the%20candidature%20of%20Imran%20Khan.%20A%20newspaper%20carried%20an%20article%20with%20the%20headline%20that%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20leaders%20were%20exiting%20the%20Congress.%E2%80%9D%20Deshpal%20says%20that%E2%80%99s%20not%20his%20quote%20but%20then%20goes%20on%20to%20ask%20why%20the%20Congress%20gives%20tickets%20only%20to%20Mevs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJ