402.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-266116%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EArchit%20has%20developed%20a%20solution%20for%20postpartum%20blood%20loss%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArchit%20has%20designed%20and%20developed%20a%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F266114%2Fmaternal-death-postpartum-haemorrhage-pph-menstrual-cup-archit-rahul-patil%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Postpartum%20Haemorrhage%20(PPH)%20cup%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20the%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98Archit%20PPH%20Cup%E2%80%99%20which%20helps%20doctors%20measure%20postpartum%20blood%20loss.%20PPH%20is%20the%20leading%20cause%20of%20maternal%20mortality%20worldwide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESon%20of%20two%20doctors%2C%20Archit%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20in%20hospitals%20and%20saw%20the%20trauma%20caused%20due%20to%20a%20mother%E2%80%99s%20death.%20He%20learnt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20single%20method%20to%20measure%20post%20delivery%20blood%20loss%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20delay%20in%20diagnosis%20and%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20for%20a%20solution%2C%20he%20designed%20the%20PPH%20cup%20using%20a%20menstrual%20cup.%20This%20cup%20gives%20doctors%20the%20exact%20volume%20of%20blood%20loss%20during%20childbirth%2C%20helping%20doctors%20manage%20PPH%2C%20during%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20golden%20hour%E2%80%9D%20(within%20one%20hour%20of%20diagnosis).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cup%20is%20made%20of%20medical%20grade%20silicone%20and%20inserted%20into%20the%20birth%20canal%20before%20or%20after%20delivery%20of%20a%20child.%20Archit%20claims%20that%20today%20nearly%2050%20hospitals%20across%20India%20are%20using%20his%20PPH%20cup%20to%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20mothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20felicitated%20with%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20in%202021%20for%20his%20life-saving%20innovation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%