.jpg%20138w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-472x1024.jpg%20472w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-708x1536.jpg%20708w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDivaa2-1688482712-150x325.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322765%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDivaa%20Uthkarsha%20is%20creating%20awareness%20about%20type%201%20diabetes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20changed%20for%20Divaa%20at%2012%2C%20when%20her%20younger%20brother%20Surya%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20Type-1%20diabetes.%20Despite%20having%20doctor%20parents%20and%20access%20to%20the%20best%20healthcare%2C%20they%20faced%20several%20challenges%20including%20stigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COther%20school%20children%20may%20not%20be%20well-informed%20and%20could%20treat%20a%20child%20with%20diabetes%20differently.%20Children%20with%20diabetes%20already%20have%20to%20cope%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20changes%2C%20such%20as%20exercise%2C%20diet%2C%20medication%2C%20glucose%20monitoring%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20her%20to%20think%20about%20how%20people%20face%20the%20challenge%20when%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20resources%20or%20awareness.%20When%20she%20joined%20the%20Future%20Leaders%20Program%20by%201M1B%20(One%20Million%20for%20One%20Billion)%2C%20she%20started%20Project%20Surya%20to%20support%20underprivileged%20children%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20who%20are%20living%20with%20Type-1%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20social%20initiative%20creates%20awareness%20and%20provides%20assistance%20to%20children%20with%20Type-1%20diabetes%20through%20awareness%2C%20advocacy%20and%20funding.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322755%2Fkarnataka-divaa-uthkarsha-project-s